{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.880", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.080", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.960", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Am Abend des 19.\u00a0Dezember 2016 verloren zw\u00f6lf Menschen aus sechs L\u00e4ndern auf dem Berliner Breitscheidplatz ihr Leben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.040", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dutzende wurden teils lebensbedrohlich verletzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.560", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es war einer der schrecklichsten Terroranschl\u00e4ge in der Geschichte unseres Landes."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.680", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Zusammenhang mit diesem Terroranschlag kam es zu Fehlern und zu Vers\u00e4umnissen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.480", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es kam zu schweren Fehlern im Umgang mit dem Attent\u00e4ter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.280", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es kam zu Vers\u00e4umnissen im Umgang mit den Hinterbliebenen und den verletzten Opfern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.840", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die CDU/CSU-Fraktion erkennt darin eine dreifache Verpflichtung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.000", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind es erstens den Opfern und den Hinterbliebenen schuldig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.760", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Vorgeschichte dieses islamistischen Terroranschlags umfassend und vorbehaltlos aufzukl\u00e4ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.640", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser Fraktionsvorsitzender Volker Kauder hat deshalb bereits im vergangenen Jahr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.760", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenige Wochen nach dem Terroranschlag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.960", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Einsetzung eines Untersuchungsausschusses angeregt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und er w\u00e4re im vergangenen Fr\u00fchjahr auch eingesetzt worden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.800", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir damals nicht bereits kurz vor dem Ende der Legislaturperiode gestanden h\u00e4tten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.680", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind es zweitens den B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrgern unseres Landes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.840", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch unseren G\u00e4sten schuldig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.080", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere Sicherheitsbeh\u00f6rden noch schlagkr\u00e4ftiger zu machen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.760", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsere Sicherheitsbeh\u00f6rden haben in \u00e4hnlich gelagerten F\u00e4llen viele Anschl\u00e4ge verhindern k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.720", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie haben herausragende Arbeit geleistet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.200", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr sind wir ihnen dankbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.400", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es ist ihnen misslungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.680", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den schlimmen Anschlag am Breitscheidplatz zu verhindern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.440", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb wollen wir mit der Aufkl\u00e4rung auch Antworten auf eine Reihe von Fragen geben: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.360", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Welche Lehren sind \u00fcber die bereits getroffenen oder vereinbarten Ma\u00dfnahmen hinaus zu ziehen mit Blick auf Befugnisse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.560", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Organisation und Kooperation der Sicherheits- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.200", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Strafverfolgungsbeh\u00f6rden von Bund und L\u00e4ndern? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.640", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Welche Konsequenzen muss der Anschlag am Breitscheidplatz f\u00fcr das Zusammenwirken von Sicherheits- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.200", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Ausl\u00e4nderbeh\u00f6rden und f\u00fcr den Vollzug des Asyl- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.440", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Ausl\u00e4nderrechts zeitigen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.640", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens ist im Zusammenhang mit dem Anschlag deutlich geworden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.600", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir den Opferschutz st\u00e4rken m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.440", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen zentrale Strukturen auf Bundesebene schaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.800", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um den Opfern einen direkten Ansprechpartner zur Verf\u00fcgung zu stellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.600", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir werden die Opferentsch\u00e4digung neu regeln."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.960", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alle angesprochenen Fragen eignen sich nicht f\u00fcr die kleinliche parteipolitische Auseinandersetzung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.840", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe deshalb bereits bei der Einbringung des Einsetzungsantrags angek\u00fcndigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.400", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die CDU/CSU-Fraktion entschlossen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.960", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Arbeit in diesem Untersuchungsausschuss im Geiste der NSU-Untersuchungsaussch\u00fcsse zu f\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.800", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dass wir uns deshalb gegen Erg\u00e4nzungen des Antrags, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.840", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den wir gemeinsam mit der SPD-Fraktion erarbeitet und vorgelegt hatten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.960", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht sperren werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.040", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den Ausschussberatungen ist der Untersuchungsauftrag nun auf Wunsch der anderen Fraktionen an einigen Stellen erg\u00e4nzt worden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.400", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einige Punkte werden ausdr\u00fccklich hervorgehoben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.400", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so etwa die Frage einer Abschiebung des Attent\u00e4ters vor dem Dezember\u00a02016, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.080", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Frage des Selbsteintrittsrechts von Bundesbeh\u00f6rden und einige weitere Gesichtspunkte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.000", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Klarer gefasst ist auch der Untersuchungszeitraum. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.480", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei der Beschreibung des Untersuchungsgegenstands wird auf Zeitangaben zu Beginn des Antrags ganz verzichtet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.120", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es wird ausdr\u00fccklich geregelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.320", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Untersuchungszeitraum erst mit der Einsetzung des Ausschusses, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.600", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also heute, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.880", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "endet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.200", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben in den vergangenen Wochen gesehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.040", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit wie viel M\u00fchen die parlamentarischen Arbeiten zur Weiterentwicklung des Untersuchungsauftrages verbunden waren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.360", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.040", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "parlamentarische Arbeit ist manchmal anstrengend. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.480", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als einzige Fraktion in diesem Haus hat sich die AfD entschlossen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "298.560", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich nicht der M\u00fche zu unterziehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "298.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.120", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einen eigenen Antrag zu erstellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "301.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "303.920", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie hat dann einen \u00c4nderungsantrag gestellt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "303.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.280", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diesen aber freilich so sp\u00e4t vorgelegt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "310.840", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass er im Berichterstattergespr\u00e4ch leider gar nicht mehr besprochen werden konnte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "310.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "312.600", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entscheidend aber ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "312.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "314.000", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die \u00fcbrigen Fraktionen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "314.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "318.200", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die den Antrag auf Einsetzung eines Untersuchungsausschusses gestellt hatten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "318.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "321.120", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf einen gemeinsamen Auftrag verst\u00e4ndigt haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "321.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "323.080", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein gutes Zeichen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "323.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "331.320", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit gibt es eine klare Arbeitsgrundlage. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "331.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "335.320", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf dieser Basis kann die Aufkl\u00e4rung gelingen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "335.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "342.920", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen die Arbeit des 1.\u00a0Untersuchungsausschusses der neuen Legislaturperiode hoffentlich zu einem Erfolg f\u00fchren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "342.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "343.760", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "343.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "347.720", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die n\u00e4chste Rednerin ist die Kollegin Dr.\u00a0Eva H\u00f6gl, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "347.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "349.960", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "SPD-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}